\n<img src=\"http://www.ctsports.com.cn/images/upload/Image/2(1).gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctsports.com.cn%2Fimages%2Fupload%2FImage%2F2%281%29.gif&h=eff18bea&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"啲人屈手腕殺球 係其實刻意咁做<br />\n定係順勢自然就會落左手腕?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"屈手腕係錯誤動作<br />\n再簡單D咁講<br />\n好似上面條女咁做時<br />\n你隻手個姿勢係好似比緊個LIKE咁<br />\n而你隻手指公本來係指住自己方向<br />\n然後臨擊球時就&quot;內旋手腕&quot;<br />\n即係將隻手指公好快咁轉去左邊<br />\n咁做既目的係將球拍扭返去正面黎擊球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rvtechnical.files.wordpress.com/2017/06/like-0.png?w=1095\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frvtechnical.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F06%2Flike-0.png%3Fw%3D1095&h=595e70a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"747250e12f39a15afd4f2f5fc13e5ad0b65062be","tid":775341,"uid":113415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad58791487a9a97967f8561dc2a7eae98ffdc08","tid":775341,"uid":52972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"701db31832a0913e2d28ee608143f7b864e0559f","tid":775341,"uid":45285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"拍拉重磅d，打幾球高遠球自然有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"終於有人講出重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算做晒樓上個位師兄講既野， 你塊板雞， D線淋， 都係無力架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話時話， 我地以前打， 係教揸柄既最後， 即係柄尾粗D個位係貼住尾指。 而家見D人打， 好多都係揸柄前邊， 即係食指差唔多去到三角椎駁住板身個位。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"呢個反手正手都有唔同架播"},{"pid":"5dc0bfe9655467b314908c203dbdf097285e1590","tid":775341,"uid":113415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:27:00.000Z","msg":"簡單講，你打波時腳要郁、腰要轉，全身轉動幫助出力而唔係純粹手腕發力，自然就唔太使用力都打到又遠又響既波。<br />\n<br />\n純粹手腕用力係你吊波、放網時候先會咁。"},{"pid":"47194391a0ec74101b71f3fa85e20366a1e6dba3","tid":775341,"